  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Calculate the kinetic energy of a particle given its mass and its velocity or momentum</item>
<item>Evaluate the kinetic energy of a body, relative to different frames of reference</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
